        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "### Side-by-Side Comparison — log K₁ ([ML]/[M][L])\n\n| Condition | Fe³⁺–EDTA (ligand_6277) | Fe³⁺–NTA (ligand_6165) | Δ log K |\n|-----------|------------------------|------------------------|---------|\n| 20 °C, I = 0.1 M, KNO₃ | **27.7** | **16.26** | +11.4 |\n| 25 °C, I = 0.1 M, KCl | **25.1** | **15.87** | +9.2 |\n| 25 °C, I = 0.5 M, KNO₃/NaClO₄ | **26.5** | **15.2** | +11.3 |\n| 25 °C, I = 1.0 M, NaClO₄ | **24.23** | **15.4–15.5** | +8.8 |",
